Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
displayScanChain(25.10)                                displayScanChain(25.10)

Name
       displayScanChain - Displays a scan chain

Syntax
       displayScanChain

       [-help]

       [<chain_name>]

       Displays  a  scan  chain. You must load the scan information, place the
       design, and view the design in the Placement view. Use this command af-
       ter scan chains are traced.

Parameters
       <chain_name>
              Specifies the scan chain.

              Default: If you do not specify this parameter, the software dis-
              plays all scan chains.

Examples
              * The following command displays all scan chains in the design:

                displayScanChain

              * The following command displays the scan chain  whose  name  is
                chain0.

                displayScanChain chain0

Related Information
              * defIn

              * defOut

              * specifyScanChain

              * report_scan_chain

